-- Russian MICEX index at its highest since March 3
-- 
-- Mon May 19, 2014 02:15AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, May 19 (Reuters) - Russia's rouble-denominated MICEX index <.MCX> rose above 1,400 points on Monday for the first time since March 3, when Moscow stocks plummeted after President Vladimir Putin received authorisation to intervene militarily in Ukraine.

